<div type="edition" xml:lang="tel-Latn" rendition="class:telugu maturity:vernacular">

<p>
<lb n="1"/>svasti śrī <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> śakavaruṣaṁbulu
<lb n="2"/>1143 gunēṇṭi Aṣāḍa śukla paṁ
<lb n="3" break="no"/>cchamiyu brihaspatavāramuna
<lb n="4"/>śrīmajjīhari śrīnarasiṁhadēva
<lb n="5" break="no"/>raku nagarānavīṭi kannamaśeṭṭi
<lb n="6"/>koḍku jagadaḷapuramuna prō
<lb n="7" break="no"/>lumudradhāri tama tallitaṁ
<lb n="8" break="no"/>ḍriki dharmmuvugāṁ beṭṭina Akhaṁ 
<lb n="9" break="no"/>ḍadīpa mokkaṇṭikiṁ beṭṭu ṭaṁkkamāḍa
<lb n="10" break="no"/>lu Ikuvaḍēnu Ī māḍalu ḍō
<lb n="11" break="no"/>sūri ceṟvunaṁ beṭṭi groppiṁcchuṭaṁ jē
<lb n="12" break="no"/>si Ī ceṟvumada<unclear>ṁ</unclear>gu ḍigguṭa sāhasa
<lb n="13" break="no"/>mallakōla puṭṭaṁḍu bhūmi phalabō
<lb n="14" break="no"/>munaṁdu nitya narasiṁhamānika mā
<lb n="15" break="no"/>naṁḍu mānya lekka Ēṁḍādiki nālvu pu
<lb n="16" break="no"/>ṭluṁ baṁdumu pratisaṁvatsaramu nā
<lb n="17" break="no"/>caṁdrārkkasthāyigāṁ jallaṁgalayadi svadattaṁ
<lb n="18"/>paradattaṁ vā yō harēti vasuṁddharāṁ <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied>
<lb n="19"/>ṣaṣṭhiṁ varṣasahasrāṇi viṣṭhāyāṁ jāya
<lb n="20" break="no"/>tē krimi[ḥ <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g>*]
</p>

